videos.description: Following a gritty 77-72 victory over 11-seed Ole Miss, 3-seed Tennessee's Kellie Harper admits Ole Miss had momentum a majority of the game.
videos.headline: Lady Vols' ability to 'never panic' was key to Harper

videos.description: Following a tough win over Ole Miss, 3-seed Tennessee's Rennia Davis says she's ready to face 2-seed South Carolina in the semifinals.
videos.headline: UT's Davis has 'full confidence' to play Gamecocks

videos.description: Despite a valiant effort by 11-seed Ole Miss, Rennia Davis (33 points, 14 rebounds) and 3-seed Tennessee stay alive to walk away with a 77-72 victory.
videos.headline: Lady Vols overcome Rebels in back-and-forth contest
